This is a prototype of the Extension:WatchGroup. Suggestions are most welcomed

Main Class
	1)'WatchGroup/WatchGroup.php' ;
Hooks
	2)'WatchGroup/WatchGroup.hooks.php' ;

Special
	3)'WatchGroup/special/SpecialWatchGroups.php' ;
		Displays all the groups og the user.
		Allows him to add groups
	4)'WatchGroup/special/SpecialWatchGroupPage.php' ;
		Displays all the pages in a particular group
	5)'WatchGroup/special/SpecialEditWatchGroups.php' ;
		Allows user to remove groups from list of WatchGroups
	6)'WatchGroup/special/SpecialWatchListToWatchGroup'
		Creates a group which contains all the pages from users WatchList
	
Action
	8)'WatchGroup/WatchedGroupItem.php' ;
	9)'WatchGroup/action/WatchGroupAction.php' ;
	
SQL
	9)'WatchGroup/sql/WatchGroup.sql' ;

API
	10)'WatchGroup/api/ApiQueryWatchGroup.php' ;
		List all the groupnames of the given user
	11)'WatchGroup/api/ApiQueryWatchGroupPages.php' ;
		List all the pages belonging to groupname(s)
		
Others
	12)WatchGroup/WatchItems.php
		Class whoch facilitates the addition of pages in groups


Working features

1)New groups can be created
2)Pages can be added to each groups by "action=watchgroup&groupname=<groupname>
3)Pages can be removed to each groups by "action=unwatchgroup&groupname=<groupname>
4)Pages can be shifted from watchlist to a particular watchgroup


I have to yet to practice MediaWiki Coding Style :-)

